ine|ja|忌宮神社|zh|Kimuya Shrine|1=Iminomiya Shrine}} || {{ill|Yamaguchi Prefecture|de|Yamaguchi Prefecture|ja|山口県|zh|Yamaguchi Prefecture}} {{ill|Shimonoseki City|de|Shimonoseki City|ja|下関市|zh|Shimonoseki City}} Chōfumiya no Uchi || Nagato Province Second Ichinomiya || |- |'''{{ill|Muraya Shrine|de|Muraya Shrine|ja|村屋神社|zh|Muraya Shrine}}'''|| murayano || Shikinai Shosha || || {{ill|Tomiya Shrine|de|Tomiya Shrine|ja|杜屋神社|zh|Tomiya Shrine}} || {{ill|Yamaguchi Prefecture|de|Yamaguchi Prefecture|ja|山口県|zh|Yamaguchi Prefecture}} {{ill|Shimonoseki City|de|Shimonoseki City|ja|下関市|zh|Shimonoseki City}}, Toyoura Town Kuroi || |}
