'''{{ill|Nagato no Shikinaisha Ichiran|de|Nagato no Shikinaisha Ichiran|ja|長門国の式内社一覧|zh|Nagato no Shikinaisha Ichiran|qq=draft}}''' (長門国の式内社一覧) is a list of {{ill|Shinto Shrines|de|Shinto Shrines|ja|神社|zh|Shinto Shrines|qq=draft}} recorded in volumes 9 and 10, "Kami Name Register: Upper and Lower," of the {{ill|Engishiki|de|Engishiki|ja|延喜式|zh|Engishiki|qq=draft}} ({{ill|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|de|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|ja|延喜式神名帳|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|zh|Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|lt=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|lt_ja=延喜式神名帳|lt_de=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|1=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|2=ja|3=延喜式神名帳|4=zh|5=延喜式神名帳|6=simple|7=Engishiki Jinmyocho|lt_zh=Engishiki Jinmyōchō|qq=draft}}) that are classified under {{ill|Nagato Province|de|Nagato Province|ja|長門国|zh|Nagato Province|qq=draft}}, comprising those shrines traditionally designated as {{ill|Shikinaisha|de|Shikinaisha|ja|式内社|1=Shikinaisha|2=ja|3=式内社|qq=draft|1=Shikinaisha|zh|Shikinaisha|qq=draft}} and their associated {{ill|Candidate Shrines|de|Candidate Shrines|ja|論社|zh|Candidate Shrines|qq=draft}}.

In addition, it also includes shrines that existed at the time of the compilation of the Engishiki Shinmeichō but which are not recorded therein, the so‐called {{ill|Shikigaisha|de|Shikigaisha|ja|式外社|1=Shikigeisha|zh|Shikigaisha|qq=draft}}.

