rines|ja|論社|1=candidate shrines|2=ja|3=論社|lt=candidate|zh|Candidate Shrines|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Candidate Shrines|13=User:Immanuelle/candidate shrines|qq=}}.
